After payment confirmation, you will receive your MTCN via email. It is fully automated.

The price list for the service:

Pay $65 = Receive $1000 FAST Clean Transfer

Pay $100 = Receive $2000 FAST Clean Transfer

Pay $200 = Receive $5000 FAST Clean Transfer

What you’ll get:

1 ) The amount you ordered

2 ) How to Withdraw Money Tutorial in PDF (with Security Tips)

Information required:

1. Name

2. Email

These details will be required when you place your order.

To open a Bank account or to make a WU transfer, you must provide your real name.

Your transfers are 100% safe. Our WU service is unbeatable. Hack attacks are not possible on your money. To receive money transfers, you will only need your ID card.

There are no more than two Western Union transactions per day that you can make with the same information. After that, Western Union will immediately close your access and remove you from the Database. The maximum transaction limit per month is 15.

We send an email to you with the MTCN code and other information once we have received your payment. in 3-5 minutes.

Once you have received the MTCN number, collect your funds.

You must pay within four hours of placing your order. Your order will be canceled if it is not completed within the given time. There is an alternative payment method for Bitcoins.

– We have the account number Western Union transfer for all countries.

– We can transfer large amounts of money. These funds can be easily transferred to wherever you need them.

– We only accept MTCN transactions of no more than 10,000 USD per week and no more than 2 per month.

– We get and pass on various transfers to our exchangers, who then give you money later. You get cash. This platform works quickly and is very reliable.

– We pay attention to every detail and don’t make mistakes during transfers.

– We will provide the MTCN number, address details, and information regarding withdrawals of funds within 20 minutes of the transfer being completed.
